Subject: [PATCH 15/19] P5040: increase the pamu size

P5040 should use 5 pamu partitions.

Signed-off-by: Haiying Wang <Haiying.Wang@freescale.com>
[Yongli: Original patch taken from FSL
    QorIQ-SDK-V1.2-SOURCE-20120614-yocto.iso image]
Integrated-by: Yongli He <yongli.he@windriver.com>
---
 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/p5040si-post.dtsi |    2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/p5040si-post.dtsi b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/p5040si-post.dtsi
index 20a41d7..25413d4 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/p5040si-post.dtsi
+++ b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/p5040si-post.dtsi
@@ -250,7 +250,7 @@
 
 	iommu@20000 {
 		compatible = "fsl,pamu-v1.0", "fsl,pamu";
-		reg = <0x20000 0x4000>;
+		reg = <0x20000 0x5000>;
 		interrupts = <
 			24 2 0 0
 			16 2 1 30>;
